TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Your second mission is to find and destroy an enemy geothermal power plant, hidden in the central crater. A base has already been built for you, ready to produce units. Make extra mexes or energy production if you need it. But be careful - the enemy may attack!

TriggerLogic.Text: Click and drag with the left mouse to select multiple units at once.
Then click and drag with the right mouse to tell them where to move.
Don't forget that you can use your com to help your lab build faster.
